An attempt to imitate the functionality of the Google Dictionary chrome extension. Also to learn the basics of extension development.

--------------------------------------------------
GOALS
--------------------------------------------------
1. Remove xulschool remnants. (Done)
2. Check inputs to avoid frivolous requests.
3. Format output to be multiple lines.
4. Make it pretty.
5. Include additional information besides primary definition/improve parsing.

HOW TO INSTALL:
1. Download the .xpi file from the bin folder.
2. Drag the file onto a firefox window.

